### ### # y = +- 1 at the poles, less than 1 in between
### ### # compute the latitude
### ### VASin $1{1} $2{1}		# elev = atan(y)	(unit sphere)
### ### # compute the longitude
### ### Compute_Longitude $1{0} $2{0} $2{2}
### ### VSMul $1{0} $1{0} 45/atan(1)
### ### VSMul $1{1} $1{1} 45/atan(1)
